claim.claim-text:
9. A process for producing cyclododecanone-O-azacyclotridecen-2-yloxime, comprising:
blending and dissolving thionyl chloride and cyclododecanone oxime in a two molar amount to thionyl chloride in the presence of a solvent;
evaporating the solvent;
adding a solvent; and
washing the resulting solution with an aqueous alkaline solution until an aqueous layer becomes alkaline.
